ActFarm Credit Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of MICHAEL F. TEES of North Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Doris Armitage Priddle, whose term has expired.
